  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/869cc231694d663bdf08fde7c5e2e07e.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/869cc231694d663bdf08fde7c5e2e07e.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Join our community on Discord to chat with the developers and other players!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/858e84db3c0ba8ce788316c83c4c0d2a.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/858e84db3c0ba8ce788316c83c4c0d2a.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world of bunny societies, existence was shattered when an evil pharmaceutical company, known for its sinister experiments, bioengineered a virus that unleashed a catastrophic zombie outbreak. In the aftermath of the outbreak, you find yourself leading a group of survivors in a world where fluffy tails and twitching noses now hide a dark and dangerous secret. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/5ac58d683645a4410fe4005c4ee4cca9.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/5ac58d683645a4410fe4005c4ee4cca9.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT TOOLS AND WEAPONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive and thrive in a post-apocalyptic world! Gather materials, craft essential tools, and create powerful weapons to defend your colony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/673f1982889ff97a1e45c05bd687a5e4.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/673f1982889ff97a1e45c05bd687a5e4.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT OFF HORDES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare your colonists to fend off waves of infected! Craft weapons, fortify your defenses, and use tactical combat to survive against ever-growing hordes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/79ae8c47756bb7a126a368b829d3d9d0.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/79ae8c47756bb7a126a368b829d3d9d0.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GROW YOUR COLONY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand and upgrade your colony by constructing new buildings, gathering essential resources, and training your colonists to improve their skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/72f824c9c9d7c2c714417990288fa2ac.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/72f824c9c9d7c2c714417990288fa2ac.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE SECRET LABORATORIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture beyond your colony into distant, dangerous worlds, searching for hidden laboratories that hold valuable research pages.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/858e84db3c0ba8ce788316c83c4c0d2a.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/858e84db3c0ba8ce788316c83c4c0d2a.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world of bunny societies, existence was shattered when an evil pharmaceutical company, known for its sinister experiments, bioengineered a virus that unleashed a catastrophic zombie outbreak. In the aftermath of the outbreak, you find yourself leading a group of survivors in a world where fluffy tails and twitching noses now hide a dark and dangerous secret. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/5ac58d683645a4410fe4005c4ee4cca9.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/5ac58d683645a4410fe4005c4ee4cca9.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT TOOLS AND WEAPONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive and thrive in a post-apocalyptic world! Gather materials, craft essential tools, and create powerful weapons to defend your colony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/673f1982889ff97a1e45c05bd687a5e4.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/673f1982889ff97a1e45c05bd687a5e4.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT OFF HORDES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare your colonists to fend off waves of infected! Craft weapons, fortify your defenses, and use tactical combat to survive against ever-growing hordes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/79ae8c47756bb7a126a368b829d3d9d0.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/79ae8c47756bb7a126a368b829d3d9d0.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GROW YOUR COLONY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand and upgrade your colony by constructing new buildings, gathering essential resources, and training your colonists to improve their skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/72f824c9c9d7c2c714417990288fa2ac.poster.avif?t=1761588207\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2596530/extras/72f824c9c9d7c2c714417990288fa2ac.webm?t=1761588207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE SECRET LABORATORIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture beyond your colony into distant, dangerous worlds, searching for hidden laboratories that hold valuable research pages.</p>",
